{"tid":1986623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局局長楊潤雄送鄧麗君嘅歌比DSE考生 係咪曲線希望佢哋終身反共?","createTime":"2020-04-24T03:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T16:47:02.000Z","uid":23707,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f428dc68c1f0818b7f8e758676f95ccb251c6ad6","tid":1986623,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"鄧麗君終身反共，熱愛中華民國，從未承認淪陷區是甚麼「新中國」。她還在法廣的訪談中明確表示，如果中國大陸維持「一黨專政的話&hellip;&hellip;它是沒甚麼希望的，沒甚麼前途的，是對整個世界來講是一個災難。」這是鄧麗君歌品、人品皆為上品的明證。"},{"pid":"6316d1088648020ff2457f8e27b520084b1d3e02","tid":1986623,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"要比藍屍知呢件事<br />\n等佢地批鬥下局長"},{"pid":"90f84451c8a39481f6fd032bbb5f3562da7c6155","tid":1986623,"uid":304281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"唔好害手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f89c916be11991151abe059a5e5f4d79ae3b146","tid":1986623,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d2ac7a832d4517d999dbb1b1bfdcac60856289","tid":1986623,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"「親愛的大陸同胞們，你們好，我是鄧麗君。我現在來到金門廣播站向大陸沿海的同胞們廣&shy;播，我今天要跟大家說的是，我很高興地能夠站在自由祖國的第一前線&mdash;&mdash;金門，我感覺到&shy;非常地快樂、非常的幸福。我希望大陸的同胞也可以跟我們享受到一樣的民主跟自由，唯有&shy;在自由、民主、富庶的生活環境下，才能擁有實現個人理想的機會；也唯有全體青年都能夠&shy;自由發揮聰明才智，國家的未來才能充滿光明和希望。我希望很快地能夠再回到金門，跟金&shy;門的弟兄們見面；當然，還有跟沿海的大陸同胞們通話。在這裡祝大家身體健康，民主萬歲&shy;！謝謝！」<br />\n<br />\n鄧麗君1991年在金門向大陸同胞喊話<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riHcC7LWIbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DriHcC7LWIbQ&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=62bec86e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riHcC7LWIbQ</a>"},{"pid":"1c7d98dee90ced876390f190a405b57e25fbe44e","tid":1986623,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a7125733a7d1587e2ba24f86e3856f6f439137","tid":1986623,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fca28482e1fe79a70adb023b09f12946961cf968","tid":1986623,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1e6ffc9d837ae9ea3003359ef73709ec970be1","tid":1986623,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a8303d3d28836c1f1a136029d94437650d34e4","tid":1986623,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}